<CD-RAT><Entry><HWD></HWD><Activity><GapFillDragDrop layer="1" h="460" w="670" y="10" x="10" wordpool-position="left"><Title alignment="left" isOn="1">Verbs for giving directions<br /></Title><Instruction alignment="left" isOn="1">Choose the correct word or phrase and drag it to the space<br /></Instruction><ReferenceObject soundIsOn="0" videoIsOn="0" defaultHeight="200" alignment="left" isOn="0" /><ScrollableAssets /><Content><Question><LineBreak size="12" /><LineBreak size="12" /><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">Hi Susie,</FONT><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">This is a quick e-mail to tell you how to get to my house. If you&apos;re driving from the south, when you get near Norwich, just </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">follow</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> the signs for the city centre and you&apos;ll </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">come</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> to a set of traffic lights near a big garage. Just go straight on and my road is on the left. You can&apos;t </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">get</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana">   lost.  </FONT><LineBreak size="13" /><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">If you&apos;re coming by train, when you get out of the station, you need to </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">cross</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> the road and </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">take</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> a number 45 bus. After the big garage at the traffic lights you should </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">get off</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> at the next stop. Then </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">keep</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> walking for about two minutes and then </FONT><Gap><Score num="1" /><FONT FACE="Verdana">turn</FONT></Gap><FONT FACE="Verdana"> left and that&apos;s my road. </FONT><LineBreak size="13" /><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">See you Saturday. Text me if you get lost! </FONT><LineBreak size="13" /><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">Love Katy. </FONT><LineBreak size="13" /><LineBreak size="13" /></Question></Content></GapFillDragDrop><Feedback playallOn="1" showAnswersOn="1" animatedFeedbackOn="1" testModeOn="0" instantFeedbackOn="0"><Sounds /></Feedback><GenericActivity hintsNextTo="0" timerIsOn="0" CDPrefsFolder="XML/" CDPrefsFile="cd.xml"><ActivityCanvas graphicAlpha="100" folder="" file="" colourAlpha="100" colour="transparent" /><SoundLibrary y="10" x="10" isOn="0" /><VideoLibrary h="265.8" w="385" y="74.2" x="10" isOn="0" /><Assets /></GenericActivity></Activity></Entry></CD-RAT>